<text top="985" left="185" width="508" height="14" font="0">This record contains the text of speeches delivered in English and of the interpretation of </text>
<text top="1000" left="185" width="513" height="14" font="0">speeches delivered in the other languages. Corrections should be submitted to the original </text>
<text top="1016" left="185" width="551" height="14" font="0">languages only. They should be incorporated in a copy of the record and sent under the signature </text>
